{
  "stem": "8.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember for three days I would not go, but eventually, I did go, and there were separate trenches for the men and the women.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, this was a very confusing time because there were no-- there was no order.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a community kitchen where women went and, and, and cooked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember eating the first time in my life fried onions on bread and how wonderful it tasted.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was surprised that we never had that before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, I organized a group of kids who decided-- of my age-- that we decided to help the old people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And especially one of the shelters was assigned for the people who were brought out from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These were old people who were-- who either had serious illnesses or were unable to take care of themselves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember how we tried to feed them, and they would spit up or they would vomit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we learned how to clean them up because they were no longer able to use the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember how, how much it took me to overcome my repulsion and do this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I also think that it helped me feel that I had a purpose, that I had done something good, and wasn't just there for nothing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One day, my grandparents, and my aunts, and uncles, and cousins were arriving from [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Italy. ?] Each day a new transport came in, and so pretty soon, we were thousands of people there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the new transport arrived on top of a hill with a train, which was outside of this area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went up there, and there was a fence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I saw my grandparents being shoved out of the-- of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
